01:14:56.116 --> 01:14:57.493
Oh, okay great.

01:14:57.534 --> 01:14:58.368
Thanks.

01:14:58.368 --> 01:14:59.036
[sighs]

01:14:59.077 --> 01:15:00.204
Just follow me, Detective.

01:15:00.245 --> 01:15:03.081
Thanks.

