[door opening]

01:15:27.189 --> 01:15:28.649
(Josie) Duncan?

01:15:34.154 --> 01:15:35.864
[sighs]

01:15:42.746 --> 01:15:44.206
Duncan?

01:15:48.752 --> 01:15:50.462
